{"tid":277054,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【一APP搞掂】八達通「好易畀」與八達通App合併","createTime":"2017-06-09T09:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-10T10:06:49.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a23a827a03b9c22e0c885084df723db46ebde6b3","tid":277054,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T09:54:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170609/large/1496994873_a0e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170609%2Flarge%2F1496994873_a0e0.jpg&h=f18115b0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n八達通旗下儲值支付工具「O!ePay 好易畀」可透過獨立手機程式進行轉賬、增值八達通及網上付款等，但由6月22日起，O!ePay App將會與八達通App合併，變相只需要一個手機App便同時處理八達通及O!ePay賬戶。<br />\n<br />\n用戶可於6月22日下載全新八達通App，或更新程式至最新版本，然後以現有密碼登入O! ePay賬戶，便可繼續使用O!ePay、查閱八達通餘額及網上付款等服務。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56805757&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170609\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56805757%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170609&d=hvP%2BnfRiAtt%2BDbsVJPhKgv%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=aa7d3153\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56805757%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170609&h=716be887\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56805757&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170609</a>"},{"pid":"3c628ca5ce84e7522e5f8cef54d6597dd781c181","tid":277054,"uid":47239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:55:06.000Z","msg":"有人用㗎咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"effe95366f514f57ffe90e8e2805254b0262ab4b","tid":277054,"uid":106363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-09T11:56:46.000Z","msg":"我部手機detect 唔到<img